&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in accounting or finance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10 years plus experience, construction experience a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CPA strongly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Industry experience as a leader

