&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary:&lt;/strong&gt; Meriton is seeking a skilled and detail-oriented Cybersecurity Analyst to join our security team. You will be responsible for monitoring and responding to security alerts, ensuring the integrity of our security infrastructure, and mitigating cyber threats. The ideal candidate will have hands-on experience with Entra ID, SIEM tools, and an EDR, along with a strong understanding of security operations and incident response.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor security alerts from SIEM and other monitoring tools, analyze threats, and respond effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Investigate and remediate security incidents, working closely with IT and other departments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and improve security incident response processes and documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
