&lt;li&gt;2+ years of experience in cybersecurity operations or a similar role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with Entra ID (formerly Azure AD), including user management and security policies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of security principles, SIEM monitoring, and incident response.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with network security, firewalls, and endpoint security tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical and problem-solving skills with an investigative mindset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Security certifications such as CompTIA Security+, CEH, or CC are a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with other security tools and platforms (e.g., EDR, XDR).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of scripting and automation via Microsoft Graph for security tasks and reporting is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
